    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 and documented with justification. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is assessed as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device in the design-phase comparative context described in the claim and requirement bindings. The assessment team unanimously accepts the model for the stated decision.",
